      <title>萨索尔火灾加剧南非对燃料进口的依赖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/sasol-fire-heightens-south-africa-s-dependence-on-fuel-imports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一场大火导致萨索尔有限公司 (Sasol Ltd.) 的 Natref 炼油厂关闭，目前南非只剩下一座原油加工厂在运营，凸显出该国对燃料进口的依赖日益加深。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/sasol-fire-heightens-south-africa-s-dependence-on-fuel-imports</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 12:25:50 GMT</pubDate>
