      <title>道富银行称，如果美国收益率达到 5%，欧元将跌至平价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/euro-to-fall-to-parity-if-us-yields-hit-5-state-street-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[道富环球投资管理公司表示，美国债券收益率上升将给欧元带来更大压力，导致欧元兑美元汇率跌至平价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/euro-to-fall-to-parity-if-us-yields-hit-5-state-street-says</guid>
